nodes.text: Zack Bossan is an author who wrote the backstory of Tannon Praji and co-wrote Ottegru Grey appearing in the Databank, through the What's The Story? feature of StarWars.com Hyperspace.
Also a frequent poster on the Star Wars message boards. His aliases are Nex: The T is Hott!!on StarWars.com, Imperial_Commandant on TheForce.net and Jerrycurl on Wookieepedia.
